  "content": "THE MESSY PART — visual with large numbers -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">The Messy Part</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 48px;\">\n    \"Just Install<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-red\">the Library\"</span>\n  </div>\n  <!-- Three problems as big visual blocks -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 28px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 80px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent-red); line-height: 1; min-width: 100px; text-align: center;\">01</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px;\">Wrong library installed</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">OpenCL drivers (for Ollama) &ne; OpenVINO runtime (for ONNX)</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 28px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 80px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent-amber); line-height: 1; min-width: 100px; text-align: center;\">02</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px;\">Missing dependency chain</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">libtbb12 not in Debian Trixie. Pulled 4 .deb files from Ubuntu Noble</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 28px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 80px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent-purple); line-height: 1; min-width: 100px; text-align: center;\">03</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px;\">Wrong library path</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">APT installs to /usr/lib/. Probe checked /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"flex: 1;\"></div>\n\n  <div class=\"warning-box\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 22px; text-align: center;\">None of them were \"hard\".<br>Used to take an afternoon — Claude handled it in minutes.</p>\n  </div>",
